<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.10">
<l>perumā vuraliṟ piṇippuṇ ṭiruntaṅ</l>
<l>kirumā maruta miṟuttavip piḷḷai</l>
<l>kurumā maṇippūṇ kulāvit tikaḻum</l>
<l>tirumār piruntavā kāṇīrē cēyiḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You with beautiful ornaments, see the way the holy chest shines resplendently</l>
<l>with ornaments of brilliant, large gems [on] this child who,</l>
<l>having been bound to a great big mortar,</l>
<l>destroyed the two large Arjuna [trees]. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
